window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The marauders, terrors from deep space, hit us hard. </p> <p>Our starships shattered. Our armies collapsed. Our cities crumbled. </p> <p>As Earth smolders, the marauders imprison us in camps. They farm us like cattle. They torture us for sport. Earth weeps. </p> <p>But there is hope. </p> <p>The Ghost Fleet, an ancient alien armada, might still exist in deep space. In a single starship, Sergeant Marco Emery and his friends seek this mythical fleet. They must find it. They must return with its might. Or the marauders will kill us all. </p>"; 
